reviews.review_text: Banger I’m listening to every MSG show in order.  Still haven’t heard the 24th and I’m only through set 1, but this is probably my favorite from the ‘88 run.  The setlist is fantastic.  Dupree’s slaps.  Ship of Fools has tons of nutsack.  Really set 1 is all nutsack.  Anyway I’m gonna go enjoy the second set.  I’ll edit this if it stinks.  I just wanna add the mastering is beautifully done as is everything Charlie Miller has done with the Pearson/Healy ultramatrixes.  Many thanks to Charlie for his tireless efforts and getting this beautiful music out to us in the pristine quality it deserves.
